---
<footer class="footer">
  <!-- Trust Banner -->
  <div class="trust-banner">
    <div class="container trust-banner-inner">
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-icon">🏆</span>
        <div class="trust-text">
          <strong>Plus de 10 ans d'expérience</strong>
          <span>Expertise reconnue à Bruxelles</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-icon">📜</span>
        <div class="trust-text">
          <strong>Toutes Certifications</strong>
          <span>Agréé Cerga, Cédicol, VCA, Mazout, Électricité</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-icon">🤝</span>
        <div class="trust-text">
          <strong>Service Garanti</strong>
          <span>100% Satisfaction, Devis transparent</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-item">
        <span class="trust-icon">⚡</span>
        <div class="trust-text">
          <strong>Intervention Rapide</strong>
          <span>Urgence 24/7 en moins de 30 minutes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h3>Kitu<span class="highlight">Plomberie</span></h3>
      <p>Votre partenaire de confiance pour tous vos travaux de plomberie et chauffage à Bruxelles. Intervention rapide, prix transparents.</p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#" aria-label="Facebook">FB</a>
        <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">IG</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Services</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/services#urgence">Dépannage Urgence 24/7</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#debouchage">Débouchage Canalisation</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#chaudiere">Entretien Chaudière</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#fuite">Recherche de Fuite</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services#sanitaire">Installation Sanitaire</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Zones</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/locations">Plombier Bruxelles Ville</a></li>
        <li><a href="/locations">Plombier Ixelles</a></li>
        <li><a href="/locations">Plombier Uccle</a></li>
        <li><a href="/locations">Plombier Anderlecht</a></li>
        <li><a href="/locations">Plombier Schaerbeek</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Contact</h4>
      <p>📞 <a href="tel:+32400000000">+32 400 00 00 00</a></p>
      <p>✉️ <a href="mailto:info@kituplomberie.be">info@kituplomberie.be</a></p>
      <p>📍 Bruxelles, Belgique</p>
      <p>TVA: BE0123.456.789</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Kitu Plomberie. Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    background-color: var(--color-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .trust-banner {
    background-color: var(--color-water-blue);
    padding: 30px 0;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .trust-banner-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  
  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
  }
  
  .trust-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .trust-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .trust-text strong {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  
  .trust-text span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .footer h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .footer h4 {
    color: var(--color-orange);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-water-blue);
  }
  
  .footer-col p {
    color: #a0aec0;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }
  
  .footer-col ul {
    list-style: none;
  }
  
  .footer-col ul li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  
  .footer-col a {
    color: #a0aec0;
  }
  
  .footer-col a:hover {
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }
  
  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  
  .social-links a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .social-links a:hover {
    background: var(--color-orange);
  }
  
  .footer-bottom {
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: #718096;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .trust-banner-inner {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 30px;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .trust-banner-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
